<plot>An American B-17 crashes behind enemy lines. Gunner David Feingold and navigator Ben Rayment are able to save themselves by parachuting. In order to escape German forces, they seek cover in an abandoned farmhouse. As Ben explores the house, he is surprised by a German deserter, Anton Kreetz. Hate, distrust and the will to survive the last days of war put the relationship of the three men to the ultimate test.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?149211</url></doc>
